                <h5 class="card-title">Employee API</h5>
                <p>
                    Following are the data API that include result in JSON format which can be used for items in Employee Management
                    such as Employee List, Employee Profile, edit and update Employee Profile
                </p>
                <p>
                    Get Employee List:
                    <a href="https://manageapi2022.azurewebsites.net/api/employee">Employee List</a>
                    <ul>
                        <li>
                            Request URL: https://manageapi2022.azurewebsites.net/api/employee/
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            Request Method: GET
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </p>
                <p>
                    Create  Employee Official Details:
                    <a href="https://manageapi2022.azurewebsites.net/api/employee/0deaf3a5-c5d0-450d-9789-8bed4a188437">Employee Official Details</a>
                    <ul>
                        <li>
                            Request URL: websiteURL + api/employee/
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            Parameters(required) : FormData
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            Request Method: POST
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </p>
                <p>
                    Get Employee Official Details:
                    <a href="https://manageapi2022.azurewebsites.net/api/employee/0deaf3a5-c5d0-450d-9789-8bed4a188437">Employee Official Details</a>
                    <ul>
                        <li>
                            Request URL: https://manageapi2022.azurewebsites.net/api/employee/id
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            Request Method: GET
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </p>
                <p>
                    Get Employee Personal Details:
                    <a href="https://manageapi2022.azurewebsites.net/api/employee/GetEmployeePersonalDetails/0deaf3a5-c5d0-450d-9789-8bed4a188437">Employee Personal Details</a>
                    <ul>
                        <li>
                            Request URL: website URL +  /api/employee/GetEmployeePersonalDetails/id
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            Request Method: GET
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </p>
                <p>
                    Update Employee Official Details:
                    <a href="https://manageapi2022.azurewebsites.net/api/employee/0deaf3a5-c5d0-450d-9789-8bed4a188437">Update Official Details</a>
                    <ul>
                        <li>
                            Request URL: website URL  + /api/employee/id
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            Request Method: PUT
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </p>
                <p>
                    Update Employee Personal Details:
                    <a href="https://manageapi2022.azurewebsites.net/api/employee/UpdateEmployeePersonalDetails/0deaf3a5-c5d0-450d-9789-8bed4a188437">Update Official Details</a>
